{{>layouts/header}}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <div class="mb-5">
                <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-4 text-primary-modern">
                    환영합니다!
                    <span class="wave">👋</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="lead text-secondary-modern mb-5">
                    MyTodos와 함께 더 스마트하게 일정을 관리하세요<br>
                    할 일 관리부터 친구와의 협업까지, 모든 것이 한 곳에!
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card-modern p-4 h-100">
                        <div class="bg-primary-modern rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3" style="width:60px;height:60px;">
                            <i class="bi bi-check2-circle text-white" style="font-size:1.5rem;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary-modern">할 일 관리</h5>
                        <p class="text-muted">직관적인 인터페이스로 할 일을 쉽게 추가하고 관리하세요</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card-modern p-4 h-100">
                        <div class="rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3" style="width:60px;height:60px; background: var(--success-color);">
                            <i class="bi bi-people text-white" style="font-size:1.5rem;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary-modern">친구와 공유</h5>
                        <p class="text-muted">친구들과 할 일을 공유하고 서로의 진행상황을 확인하세요</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card-modern p-4 h-100">
                        <div class="rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3" style="width:60px;height:60px; background: var(--accent-color);">
                            <i class="bi bi-calendar3 text-white" style="font-size:1.5rem;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary-modern">캘린더 뷰</h5>
                        <p class="text-muted">월별 캘린더로 한눈에 일정을 파악하고 계획을 세우세요</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row justify-content-center gap-3">
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary-modern btn-lg px-5 py-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right me-2"></i>로그인
                </a>
                <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-success-modern btn-lg px-5 py-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-person-plus me-2"></i>회원가입
                </a>
                <a href="/todos" class="btn btn-secondary-modern btn-lg px-5 py-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-list-task me-2"></i>둘러보기
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card-modern p-4 text-center">
                <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2017/01/10/19/05/checklist-1973223_1280.png"
                     alt="todo illustration"
                     class="img-fluid rounded"
                     style="max-height: 300px; object-fit: contain; filter: grayscale(20%);">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .wave {
        animation: wave 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes wave {
        0%, 100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
        25% { transform: rotate(20deg); }
        75% { transform: rotate(-10deg); }
    }
</style>

{{>layouts/footer}}
